A4.text: She was christened Carmen by her father because of his love for Bizet's Carmen.

A5.text: Miranda was born Maria do Carmo Miranda da Cunha in 1909 in Várzea da Ovelha e Aliviada, a village in the northern Portuguese municipality of Marco de Canaveses.
